@79=~Look at Ignus. He is going to wreak havoc, likely as much among enemies as among allies.~
@80=~There is no time. You are almost there.~
@82=~The skull shares your glance and flips one eyeball around. The lack of eyelids makes it difficult to wink, but Morte does his best.~
@83=~"I won't let you down, chief." ~ [MRT110]
@84=~You look away from Morte and glance ahead to check the distance to the Foundry.~
@86=~You are alone in this. Your temporary allies lie in wait where the smoke bellows. It is almost time.~
