@93=~Look at Ignus. He is going to wreak havoc, likely as much among enemies as among allies.~
@94=~There is no time. You are almost there.~
@96=~Annah recognizes the meaning of your glance without any hesitation. She gives you a confident smile and whips her tail provocatively.~
@97=~You look away from Annah and glance ahead to check the distance to the Foundry.~
@99=~You are alone in this. Your temporary allies lie in wait where the smoke bellows. It is almost time.~
