@106=~Look at Ignus. He is going to wreak havoc, likely as much among enemies as among allies.~
@107=~There is no time. You are almost there.~
@109=~Your eyes meet for a moment, but Grace quickly turns her gaze away. She seems saddened by the circumstances. Still, you know she will be there, doing what she does best.~
@110=~You look away from Fall-from-Grace and glance ahead to check the distance to the Foundry.~
@112=~You are alone in this. Your temporary allies lie in wait where the smoke bellows. It is almost time.~
@113=~Look at Dak'kon. A fighter whose strategy and calm may turn the tide of battle.~
@114=~Look at Morte. He has been by your side from the start. He is fast and can get into places no one else can. He could be crucial in surprise attacks.~
