@119=~Look at Ignus. He is going to wreak havoc, likely as much among enemies as among allies.~
@120=~There is no time. You are almost there.~
@122=~Nordom does not understand the need for discretion. He whirrs and clicks.~
@123=~"New directive for Nordom? Awaiting confirmation." ~ [MODRO01]
@125=~"Yes, Nordom. Take the high ground and hold it. Stay out of trouble."~
@127=~Nordom bobs up and down.~
@128=~"Affirmative." The rogue modron does not seem to have any additional comments or doubts. ~ [NOR089]
@129=~You look away from Nordom and glance ahead to check the distance to the Foundry.~
@131=~You are alone in this. Your temporary allies lie in wait where the smoke bellows. It is almost time.~
@132=~Look at Dak'kon. A fighter whose strategy and calm may turn the tide of battle.~
@133=~Look at Morte. He has been by your side from the start. He is fast and can get into places no one else can. He could be crucial in surprise attacks.~
